<div class="jp-InputArea jp-Cell-inputArea"><div class="jp-InputPrompt jp-InputArea-prompt">
</div><div class="jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOutput " data-mime-type="text/markdown">
<ul>
<li>"pattern" field is the substring used in SQL like queries: "select ... from TABLE1 where textfield like '%{pattern}%'</li>
<li>count is the number of rows in the query result.</li>
<li>no_index_time is the query time in milliseconds by the MySQL RDBMS without nCharIndex.</li>
<li>index_time is the query time in milliseconds with help from nCharIndex.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="Observations">Observations<a class="anchor-link" href="#Observations">&#182;</a></h3><ul>
<li>no_index_time is almost the same around 10000ms, regardless of pattern length and count.</li>
<li>index_time is positively correlated with count. </li>
</ul>
<h3 id="Performance-advantage">Performance advantage<a class="anchor-link" href="#Performance-advantage">&#182;</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
</div>
