<p>No wonder it exceeded leetcode's time limit.</p>
<p>Reading the code, we can see it's a modified dijkstra algorithm. Most of the computations probably happens in the while loop, and the for loop inside the while loop.</p>
<p>However, the apparent is not always right. Let's do some profiling!</p>
